branch; 
<emphasis id="0B93EA88FFD52C33FCF7051D233EE8AD" bold="true" box="[789,807,1914,1933]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">B.</emphasis>
Inflorescence; 
<emphasis id="0B93EA88FFD52C33FC50051D23DDE8AD" bold="true" box="[946,964,1914,1933]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">C.</emphasis>
Flower post-anthesis. [
<emphasis id="0B93EA88FFD52C33FF6C05F32172E887" box="[142,363,1940,1959]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Antilahimena et al. 1540</emphasis>
